GNotes!
----------

Vague Instructions:

In the Gnotes applet:
  left button       - create a new note
  middle button     - move the applet
  right button      - bring up the applet menu

On each note's handle:
  left button       - move the note
  shift left button - resize the note
  middle button     - create a new note
  right button      - bring up the note menu

